26:51.380 --> 26:52.680
Hello.

26:52.680 --> 26:55.230
Inquiry of financial transaction details...

26:55.230 --> 26:57.790
inquiry of international travel records...

26:57.790 --> 26:59.760
and inquiry about call details.

26:59.760 --> 27:01.110
Gosh...

27:02.310 --> 27:05.000
