31:07.290 --> 31:09.540
What problems?

31:09.540 --> 31:10.660
First,

31:10.660 --> 31:13.790
discovery isn't mandatory but encouraged.

31:13.790 --> 31:15.530
If they insist on not doing it,

31:15.530 --> 31:19.240
then we have no way of forcing them.

31:19.240 --> 31:20.870
Second,

31:20.870 --> 31:23.990
if they do the test...

31:23.990 --> 31:26.180
and it's not sexual dysfunction...

31:26.180 --> 31:27.020
If it's not?

31:27.020 --> 31:30.560
There's a chance he could be fine
when getting tested at the hospital.

31:30.560 --> 31:32.260
If it's psychology-related anyway,

31:32.260 --> 31:35.810
it might be a problem with
your relationship. In that case,

31:35.810 --> 31:39.050
