31:47.980 --> 31:49.550
What about you?

31:49.550 --> 31:51.210
What are you doing?

31:51.210 --> 31:53.710
You claimed to be an
expert in male problems.

31:53.710 --> 31:56.930
You should contribute something, too.

31:56.930 --> 31:59.460
You insisted it was a 100 percent affair,

31:59.460 --> 32:01.410
but you haven't discovered anything.

32:01.410 --> 32:02.110
- Well...
- She's right.

32:02.110 --> 32:03.610
She's right.

32:03.610 --> 32:06.980
I agreed to the joint appointment because
you said a man knows men's issues.

32:06.980 --> 32:09.500
