32:27.290 --> 32:29.990
If you want to win, just take the test.

32:29.990 --> 32:32.130
No, don't get the test.

32:32.130 --> 32:33.810
You...

32:33.810 --> 32:36.710
You do know what you're saying, right?

32:36.710 --> 32:38.740
Yes, of course.

32:39.230 --> 32:42.620
Sang Eun, could you give me
your husband's phone number?

32:42.620 --> 32:45.590
