33:34.640 --> 33:36.550
Did your attorney tell you to?

33:36.550 --> 33:40.680
Wait... why should I tell you that?

33:40.680 --> 33:42.270
Did you come here to sound it out?

33:42.270 --> 33:47.100
Sir. I just want to help you.

33:47.100 --> 33:49.340
