he would've even confessed to you.

57:07.330 --> 57:08.750
Hey.

57:10.810 --> 57:12.200
Huh?

57:12.200 --> 57:14.870
Spewing nonsense every
time you open your mouth.

57:14.870 --> 57:16.320
Hey,

57:16.320 --> 57:17.950
lettuce is expensive these days.

57:17.950 --> 57:19.150
What are you saying?

57:19.150 --> 57:21.180
I hate it. Absolutely hate it.

57:21.180 --> 57:22.540
- Auntie...
- I hate it.

57:22.540 --> 57:23.960
Auntie!

57:32.600 --> 57:34.670
Hey, Sang Eun.

57:37.920 --> 57:39.340
What?

57:41.410 --> 57:42.920
Hey,

57:42.920 --> 57:45.040
are you sure you won't regret this?

57:45.040 --> 57:46.290
Who knows?

57:46.290 --> 57:48.900
I might end up regretting this.

57:48.900 --> 57:53.650
But every decision comes with a price.

57:53.650 --> 57:56.990
If regret is the cost,
then I have no choice.

57:56.990 --> 57:59.090
Ha Ra.

58:02.890 --> 58:04.570
The key.

58:22.830 --> 58:25.430
Mr. Kim Mu Jin...

58:25.430 --> 58:28.910
no longer wants to meet the other party.

58:28.910 --> 58:32.090
Let's just quickly proceed with
the adjustments by ourselves.

58:32.090 --> 58:36.680
I'll apply for the earliest
date for adjustments.

58:36.680 --> 58:38.160
Aigoo,

58:38.160 --> 58:40.030
how bittersweet.

58:40.030 --> 58:42.730
No matter how many times
I go through divorce cases,

58:42.730 --> 58:47.270
