Huh?

59:07.650 --> 59:09.350
Look here-

59:12.680 --> 59:14.250
Ahjussi,

59:16.020 --> 59:17.190
if...

59:18.200 --> 59:20.090
there's a problem with your package,

59:20.090 --> 59:23.500
how about getting treatment at a hospital?

59:24.390 --> 59:26.510
Even if you claim depression,

59:26.510 --> 59:29.520
paranoia, or mental and physical
weakness due to sexual dysfunction,

59:29.520 --> 59:31.220
we won't negotiate...

59:31.220 --> 59:34.380
your settlement money out of pity.

59:35.210 --> 59:37.200
The transcript of...

59:37.200 --> 59:41.870
a conversation with the direct participation
of the involved party isn't illegal evidence.

59:41.870 --> 59:43.510
You know that, right?

