About what?

1:00:19.930 --> 1:00:22.040
To be honest,

1:00:22.040 --> 1:00:24.790
I lived without thinking about you.

1:00:24.790 --> 1:00:28.590
I had zero interest in what you were up to

1:00:28.590 --> 1:00:30.820
